WEBVTT

01:51.740 --> 01:57.600
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.550 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 15]

02:05.350 --> 02:06.480
Young Master Qiyan.

02:06.870 --> 02:08.400
Why are you still here?

02:09.430 --> 02:11.140
Care to have a couple of drinks with me?

02:11.140 --> 02:12.930
The moonlight tonight is so beautiful,

02:12.930 --> 02:14.450
yet I'm drinking alone.

02:14.520 --> 02:15.910
It's truly lonely.

02:16.870 --> 02:17.750
I can't.

02:18.630 --> 02:19.950
If I drink too much,

02:20.130 --> 02:21.760
how am I supposed to study?

02:24.430 --> 02:25.940
What exactly are you so busy with

02:25.940 --> 02:28.600
that you'd rather waste
such a beautiful night?

02:29.520 --> 02:30.730
Young Master Qiyan,

02:30.750 --> 02:31.910
don't you know?

02:32.290 --> 02:33.450
Maybe I can

02:33.480 --> 02:35.410
take the selection exam this year.

02:36.910 --> 02:38.310
So this is what you told me

02:38.310 --> 02:39.640
you wanted to do before?

02:42.430 --> 02:44.490
Why make things so hard for yourself?

02:44.660 --> 02:45.260
I...

02:55.410 --> 02:57.340
You are the one making things hard.

02:58.720 --> 03:00.580
Just go back, Young Master Qiyan.

03:07.100 --> 03:09.010
What a waste of good wine.

03:16.270 --> 03:19.240
[Juyun Gate]

03:23.680 --> 03:25.680
I'm sure you all are already aware of

03:25.870 --> 03:27.840
the draft proposal for
the selection exam reform.

03:27.840 --> 03:30.370
This matter should not be delayed
any longer.

03:30.590 --> 03:31.430
Let's

03:32.000 --> 03:33.680
make a final statement today.

03:39.440 --> 03:40.550
Your Excellency.

03:43.030 --> 03:44.360
Regarding this matter,

03:45.990 --> 03:48.380
I have said everything there is to say,

03:49.150 --> 03:51.079
and I no longer wish to be involved.

03:52.440 --> 03:53.390
You guys

03:54.520 --> 03:57.180
may proceed with your statements
as you please.

04:00.150 --> 04:01.150
Your Excellency.

04:01.780 --> 04:03.590
What Zheng means is that

04:03.610 --> 04:06.810
the selection exam is a matter
of the younger generation.

04:07.080 --> 04:08.580
Us old folks

04:08.730 --> 04:11.800
are no longer able to grasp its essence.

04:12.620 --> 04:13.520
These matters should be left

04:13.520 --> 04:16.310
to you younger generation to handle.

04:18.160 --> 04:21.360
You certainly wouldn't
throw your weight around, right?

04:27.520 --> 04:28.430
Your Excellency.

04:28.430 --> 04:29.480
I concur.

04:32.300 --> 04:35.190
Since the Three Elders have shown
such noble integrity,

04:35.190 --> 04:36.270
I hope you all

04:36.270 --> 04:38.600
won't disappoint their good intentions.

04:39.530 --> 04:40.320
Today,

04:40.750 --> 04:43.550
everyone may freely express
their true thoughts.

04:43.850 --> 04:44.650
Let's begin.

05:09.460 --> 05:11.590
The draft reform of the selection exam

05:11.990 --> 05:13.990
shall be implemented immediately!

05:20.870 --> 05:23.600
Today is your big day.

05:23.910 --> 05:26.310
I will take the exam
in this women's attire.

05:36.340 --> 05:38.090
Then this armor

05:38.510 --> 05:39.810
suits you perfectly.

05:41.120 --> 05:42.720
It's yours from now on.

05:53.390 --> 05:55.360
Why did you change your minds again?

05:55.360 --> 05:56.580
Why do you regard this exam reform

05:56.580 --> 05:57.850
as some terrible scourge

05:57.850 --> 05:59.580
and try to avoid it at all costs?

06:02.320 --> 06:03.850
As the ancient saying goes,

06:03.920 --> 06:04.650
propriety is

06:04.890 --> 06:06.680
the principle of heaven,

06:06.710 --> 06:08.310
the righteousness of earth,

06:08.600 --> 06:10.280
and the conduct of the people.

06:10.320 --> 06:11.820
If propriety is not established,

06:11.820 --> 06:14.950
the people will lose
a clear standard for their conduct.

06:15.010 --> 06:17.710
The profound harm it causes
would be immeasurable.

06:17.710 --> 06:18.910
Stop, stop.

06:19.710 --> 06:22.220
My ears are getting calluses
from hearing this.

06:22.220 --> 06:24.930
I have already explained the pros and cons
of this exam reform

06:24.930 --> 06:26.690
to all of you clearly.

06:27.360 --> 06:29.410
Why are you still so stubborn?

06:29.430 --> 06:30.700
A national selection exam

06:30.700 --> 06:32.180
does indeed have its merits,

06:32.180 --> 06:33.780
and its effects are visible.

06:34.030 --> 06:35.560
However, there is one point

06:35.730 --> 06:36.400
that I

06:36.690 --> 06:37.750
cannot agree with.

06:37.890 --> 06:39.740
Are you referring to the inclusion
of women in the selection exams?

06:39.740 --> 06:40.450
Exactly.

06:41.070 --> 06:43.950
Women serving as officials goes against
human ethics and established norms.

06:43.950 --> 06:44.680
I'd like to ask:

06:44.680 --> 06:47.080
if all women in the world
devote themselves

06:47.250 --> 06:49.570
to official careers like men do,

06:49.680 --> 06:50.350
then

06:50.510 --> 06:51.700
who will manage

06:51.730 --> 06:53.220
the household affairs?

06:53.690 --> 06:55.420
And who will bear the responsibility

06:55.420 --> 06:57.150
of continuing the family line?

06:57.380 --> 06:58.060
Moreover,

06:58.090 --> 07:00.260
women showing their faces
in the officialdom

07:00.260 --> 07:01.770
will inevitably draw attention,

07:01.770 --> 07:02.790
which would cause

07:02.960 --> 07:05.320
the men in their families
to live in constant anxiety.

07:05.320 --> 07:08.490
This move will bring nothing but harm.

07:08.510 --> 07:09.220
Therefore,

07:09.250 --> 07:10.910
as long as Your Excellency
simply crosses out

07:10.910 --> 07:13.160
the words "regardless of gender",

07:13.210 --> 07:15.770
restricting the selection exams
to men only,

07:15.800 --> 07:17.800
we will have no further objections.

07:18.230 --> 07:20.310
What if I insist on this today?

07:20.840 --> 07:23.900
We ask Your Excellency to revise
the inclusion of women

07:24.390 --> 07:25.410
in the selection exams. Otherwise,

07:25.410 --> 07:26.300
we

07:27.550 --> 07:30.280
would rather resign
and return to our hometowns.

07:48.390 --> 07:50.320
His Excellency hereby proclaims:

07:50.460 --> 07:53.800
Considering that our Nine Cities
are blessed with outstanding people

07:53.800 --> 07:55.659
and abundant talent,

07:56.340 --> 07:58.370
yet there has long been no proper path
to official service

07:58.370 --> 07:59.800
and no hope for people to serve the state,

07:59.800 --> 08:01.920
this is truly painful.

08:02.550 --> 08:04.510
Out of compassion for the people,

08:04.540 --> 08:06.270
I hereby initiate this reform.

08:06.740 --> 08:08.620
All citizens of the Nine Cities,

08:08.650 --> 08:10.470
regardless of status, wealth, or region,

08:10.470 --> 08:11.810
who are deemed capable may participate.

08:11.810 --> 08:13.880
Starting tomorrow, all citizens
of the Nine Cities—

08:13.880 --> 08:14.930
except women—

08:15.060 --> 08:19.330
may go to Ling'an Examination Academy
to register and collect an Exam Token.

08:19.680 --> 08:24.170
With this token, they shall be eligible to
participate in this year's selection exam.

08:24.170 --> 08:31.090
-Great!
-Great!

08:31.620 --> 08:35.010
In the end, women still cannot
take the selection exam.

08:45.000 --> 08:46.030
Fan Yun,

08:46.050 --> 08:47.600
say whatever you want to say.

08:47.600 --> 08:49.200
Cry or make a fuss if you want.

08:49.620 --> 08:51.350
Just don't be hard on yourself.

08:52.010 --> 08:52.970
Yun.

08:53.320 --> 08:55.620
Most things in life don't go as we wish.

08:55.910 --> 08:58.640
Maybe what feels like a huge deal today

08:59.120 --> 09:00.060
will mean nothing

09:00.060 --> 09:01.180
by tomorrow.

09:03.850 --> 09:04.940
Yun.

09:05.630 --> 09:06.710
How about I

09:07.200 --> 09:09.120
treat you guys to Huan'e House

09:09.390 --> 09:09.990
for a meal?

09:10.850 --> 09:13.250
You've always loved the food there, right?

09:14.190 --> 09:14.800
Wanna go?

09:20.850 --> 09:22.640
Dad, Gao Ran.

09:24.650 --> 09:27.280
I want to have some quiet time to myself

09:28.040 --> 09:29.640
and be alone for a while.

09:30.470 --> 09:32.070
Please go back to your rooms.

09:32.190 --> 09:34.020
Well, it's good that you want to sleep.

09:34.020 --> 09:35.280
Maybe when you wake up,

09:35.290 --> 09:37.320
everything will have taken a turn
for the better,

09:37.320 --> 09:37.840
right?

09:37.840 --> 09:38.440
Yun,

09:38.440 --> 09:39.910
sleep as long as you want.

09:39.910 --> 09:41.440
You are at home. No one will bother you.

09:41.440 --> 09:42.920
Don't think about anything.

09:42.920 --> 09:44.580
I'll take care of everything.

09:44.610 --> 09:45.560
I'm here for you,

09:45.590 --> 09:46.360
alright?

09:46.900 --> 09:47.600
Yun?

09:48.040 --> 09:49.400
-Lord Fan Qi.
-Let me tell you...

09:49.400 --> 09:50.280
-Come on.
-Wait...

09:50.280 --> 09:51.870
-I...
-That's enough.

09:51.890 --> 09:54.730
Yun, how about eating something
before you sleep?

09:55.520 --> 09:56.210
Yun?

10:02.070 --> 10:03.420
Now that His Excellency has opened up
the selection exam,

10:03.420 --> 10:05.310
everyone has a chance
to become an official.

10:05.310 --> 10:06.100
Maybe

10:06.150 --> 10:08.300
I could even get a minor post
at the Qi Residence.

10:08.300 --> 10:10.610
I'm better at grazing horses
than those noble young heirs anyway.

10:10.610 --> 10:11.940
I'm especially good at using the abacus.

10:11.940 --> 10:14.300
Getting into the Commerce Bureau
to keep ledgers should be no problem.

10:14.300 --> 10:15.380
Okay, next.

10:16.210 --> 10:17.130
Tian Xing.

10:17.720 --> 10:19.510
Okay. This is your Exam Token.

10:28.950 --> 10:29.950
Your Excellency.

10:30.120 --> 10:32.000
The reform decree for the selection exam

10:32.000 --> 10:33.600
has been posted in Ling'an City,
and the decrees

10:33.600 --> 10:36.560
for the outer cities are also being
urgently dispatched by fast horses.

10:36.560 --> 10:37.290
Got it.

10:39.330 --> 10:42.400
I heard the whole city turns out,
and the streets are packed with people—

10:42.400 --> 10:44.730
even more lively than during the New Year.

10:46.120 --> 10:48.300
Your Excellency, don't you want to
go out for a walk

10:48.300 --> 10:50.030
and celebrate with the people?

10:53.190 --> 10:54.430
You may leave now.

10:55.080 --> 10:56.780
I want to be alone for a while.

11:35.030 --> 11:36.160
Young Master Qiyan.

11:37.920 --> 11:39.010
It seems

11:39.040 --> 11:40.550
in the coming days,

11:40.630 --> 11:42.290
your profits will skyrocket.

11:43.330 --> 11:44.750
You have a keen eye, Young Master.

11:44.750 --> 11:46.440
The Governor has opened up
the selection exam to everyone,

11:46.440 --> 11:48.360
so people are no longer
restricted by their birth.

11:48.360 --> 11:49.450
Naturally, this has given everyone

11:49.450 --> 11:51.020
new hope.

11:51.050 --> 11:51.670
Therefore,

11:51.670 --> 11:53.510
they are all coming to buy books
and study hard,

11:53.510 --> 11:54.330
all in hopes of

11:54.430 --> 11:57.090
changing their fate
through their own efforts.

11:57.790 --> 11:58.820
So it seems

11:58.840 --> 12:01.000
the Governor's measures
have won public support.

12:01.000 --> 12:01.730
Yes, indeed.

12:02.550 --> 12:04.370
I didn't expect the Governor
to be so attuned to

12:04.370 --> 12:06.400
the people's needs at such a young age.

12:06.400 --> 12:08.030
Just this idea of
treating everyone equally,

12:08.030 --> 12:10.690
bridging the gap
between commoners and nobles—

12:10.690 --> 12:12.290
this move by the Governor

12:12.320 --> 12:15.200
can truly be said to be unprecedented.

12:15.320 --> 12:16.840
He really is a wise ruler.

12:20.360 --> 12:21.080
Is that so?

12:21.850 --> 12:22.800
Absolutely.

12:23.810 --> 12:24.820
In that case,

12:25.340 --> 12:27.070
how about I close down your shop

12:27.080 --> 12:29.210
so you can take the selection exam too?

12:30.360 --> 12:31.080
Young Master Qiyan,

12:31.080 --> 12:32.270
I misspoke.

12:32.960 --> 12:34.030
I-I lost my head for a moment.

12:34.030 --> 12:35.240
Please punish me.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.030
Enough.

12:36.430 --> 12:37.270
You may leave.

12:37.720 --> 12:41.180
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.

12:56.530 --> 12:58.920
Why are there only male customers
in the shop?

12:58.920 --> 13:00.360
Isn't this a national selection exam?

13:00.360 --> 13:02.730
There should be women coming to
buy books as well, shouldn't there?

13:02.730 --> 13:04.130
Don't you know, Boss?

13:04.460 --> 13:05.650
This year's selection exam reform
removes distinctions of

13:05.650 --> 13:07.440
region and of nobility versus commoners,

13:07.440 --> 13:08.640
but it does distinguish
between men and women.

13:08.640 --> 13:10.330
Women, whether commoners or nobles,

13:10.330 --> 13:11.990
are not eligible to take part.

13:38.270 --> 13:39.020
Come out.

13:45.070 --> 13:46.070
Your Excellency.

13:47.920 --> 13:48.980
Since you're here,

13:49.150 --> 13:50.750
why not go inside and see her?

13:51.130 --> 13:52.160
How is Fan Yun?

13:52.820 --> 13:53.760
She's feeling a bit low.

13:53.760 --> 13:56.620
She'll feel better
after sleeping until tomorrow.

13:58.390 --> 13:59.190
That's good.

14:00.140 --> 14:00.770
Let's go.

14:01.010 --> 14:02.470
I'll take you in to see her.

14:04.030 --> 14:05.120
I won't go in.

14:06.120 --> 14:07.720
It's good to know she's fine.

14:08.440 --> 14:09.640
Let her get some rest.

14:11.150 --> 14:12.280
Then what about you?

14:13.210 --> 14:14.290
Did you rest well?

14:16.120 --> 14:17.980
Have you not slept for days again?

14:21.870 --> 14:22.750
I can't sleep.

14:25.140 --> 14:27.070
You two are very similar in one way.

14:27.100 --> 14:27.910
That is,

14:28.440 --> 14:31.130
you're both considerate of
everyone around you,

14:31.130 --> 14:32.610
but hard on yourselves.

14:32.720 --> 14:34.580
Why put yourselves through that?

14:39.000 --> 14:39.840
I just

14:41.890 --> 14:43.350
don't know how to face her.

14:45.530 --> 14:48.100
You should have told her what happened.

14:48.130 --> 14:49.730
Even if it failed,

14:49.840 --> 14:51.970
at least she would have been prepared.

14:53.550 --> 14:55.010
You know Fan Yun.

14:55.140 --> 14:56.740
No matter what she does,

14:56.770 --> 14:58.250
she always gives her all.

14:59.960 --> 15:01.030
It's just that

15:01.200 --> 15:02.450
preparing for the selection exam

15:02.450 --> 15:04.220
already exhausted her.

15:04.950 --> 15:07.670
If the officials' disputes
had troubled her further,

15:07.670 --> 15:09.200
I really couldn't bear it.

15:10.640 --> 15:11.690
Besides,

15:12.000 --> 15:13.660
what the officials opposed the most
this time

15:13.660 --> 15:15.390
was women becoming officials.

15:15.390 --> 15:17.110
If she had been there to lobby,

15:17.150 --> 15:19.150
it would have only caused bigger disputes.

15:19.150 --> 15:21.350
Not only would it have failed
to achieve the desired effect,

15:21.350 --> 15:23.170
but it would also have easily
brought trouble upon her,

15:23.170 --> 15:24.890
making her a target of their criticism.

15:24.890 --> 15:26.460
So, Your Excellency didn't explain.

15:26.460 --> 15:29.090
Even if it caused a misunderstanding
between you and Fan Yun,

15:29.090 --> 15:30.290
you would still do it?

15:37.490 --> 15:38.730
I had no other choice.

15:40.320 --> 15:42.280
If she really gets mad at me,

15:42.590 --> 15:44.120
I'll just have to accept it.

15:45.510 --> 15:46.910
Take good care of Fan Yun.

16:12.050 --> 16:13.380
Are you feeling better?

16:13.660 --> 16:15.310
Thank you, Young Master Qiyan.

16:15.310 --> 16:16.910
I'm feeling much better now.

16:21.750 --> 16:22.880
Young Master Qiyan,

16:22.910 --> 16:24.270
what is it that you wanted

16:24.270 --> 16:25.490
to see me for?

16:27.840 --> 16:29.570
What do you think of this place?

16:30.780 --> 16:31.870
Here?

16:33.570 --> 16:34.570
It's pretty good.

16:34.910 --> 16:36.420
Same as before.

16:37.720 --> 16:39.050
But that's only for now.

16:43.840 --> 16:44.870
What's this?

16:45.780 --> 16:47.040
Open it and take a look.

16:51.790 --> 16:53.400
A layout map?

16:55.510 --> 16:57.640
I plan to rebuild a West Market here.

16:58.360 --> 17:01.020
All the shops will be
redesigned and renovated.

17:01.150 --> 17:02.420
Once it's done,

17:02.510 --> 17:03.320
it will be

17:03.320 --> 17:05.380
the most bustling market in the city.

17:05.770 --> 17:07.240
What you see on the scroll

17:07.349 --> 17:09.480
is what it will look like in the future.

17:09.589 --> 17:10.750
What do you think?

17:12.440 --> 17:14.589
I think...

17:18.510 --> 17:20.660
I think the current West Market,

17:20.690 --> 17:22.339
though it looks messy,

17:22.359 --> 17:23.780
has a human touch.

17:24.109 --> 17:25.040
Every shop

17:25.069 --> 17:27.030
tries its best to attract customers.

17:27.030 --> 17:28.290
It's really lively.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.680
But on your map,

17:30.680 --> 17:32.700
it's bare and empty,

17:32.960 --> 17:35.530
and every shop looks exactly the same.

17:35.830 --> 17:37.790
Won't that be too dull?

17:40.170 --> 17:42.010
Then tear it up. I'll find someone else
to redesign it.

17:42.010 --> 17:43.280
Don't, don't.

17:43.880 --> 17:45.920
I'm just sharing my thoughts.

17:47.110 --> 17:49.710
These shops belong to you,
Young Master Qiyan.

17:50.070 --> 17:51.680
So the decision's up to you.

17:52.640 --> 17:53.310
No.

17:54.530 --> 17:55.690
From now on,

17:56.070 --> 17:57.530
these shops are all yours.

18:00.170 --> 18:01.260
Mine?

18:02.690 --> 18:03.200
This...

18:04.340 --> 18:05.060
This...

18:06.210 --> 18:07.540
Young Master Qiyan,

18:07.570 --> 18:09.090
please stop joking.

18:09.640 --> 18:11.440
I've done nothing to deserve it.

18:13.110 --> 18:15.290
I know you won't accept gifts
for no reason.

18:15.290 --> 18:16.330
So I want

18:16.360 --> 18:17.820
you to be the manager here.

18:18.560 --> 18:20.560
From now on, you'll be the Number Two

18:20.990 --> 18:22.050
of Juyun Pavilion.

18:28.140 --> 18:30.310
So what if you can't take
the selection exam?

18:30.310 --> 18:31.510
With your abilities,

18:31.640 --> 18:34.500
you can succeed in
anything you want to do anywhere.

18:34.660 --> 18:36.030
You want a chance—

18:36.920 --> 18:38.580
and I'll give you that chance.

18:41.070 --> 18:42.000
I...

18:44.410 --> 18:45.380
Every shop,

18:45.410 --> 18:46.040
backyard,

18:46.060 --> 18:47.120
and delivery route

18:47.270 --> 18:49.310
will be redesigned and renovated.

18:50.190 --> 18:51.450
Scenes of disorder and filth

18:51.450 --> 18:52.980
will never appear again.

18:54.350 --> 18:55.070
Hurry up.

18:55.460 --> 18:56.500
Sorry, sorry.

18:56.520 --> 18:57.360
The frost was heavy last night.

18:57.360 --> 18:59.370
We students didn't sleep until morning.

18:59.370 --> 19:00.220
We'll leave right away.

19:00.220 --> 19:01.210
We didn't mean to disturb you.

19:01.210 --> 19:02.360
We'll just pack up and leave.

19:02.360 --> 19:03.640
We're really sorry.

19:05.150 --> 19:05.900
Wait.

19:07.310 --> 19:08.200
Are you

19:08.410 --> 19:09.490
all students?

19:09.980 --> 19:10.940
I am ashamed.

19:10.960 --> 19:12.840
We are all students from Gao City Academy,

19:12.840 --> 19:14.480
here to take the selection exam.

19:14.480 --> 19:16.640
Who would have thought that
there would be so many candidates

19:16.640 --> 19:18.310
preparing for the exam in Ling'an

19:18.310 --> 19:19.640
that the inns in the city

19:19.640 --> 19:20.570
are in short supply,

19:20.570 --> 19:22.200
and they've actually
raised their prices arbitrarily.

19:22.200 --> 19:23.920
Even the cheapest inns in the city

19:23.920 --> 19:25.090
now cost 10 taels of silver.

19:25.090 --> 19:25.730
Ten...

19:26.150 --> 19:27.910
We all come from poor families

19:27.930 --> 19:29.160
and are short on money,

19:29.160 --> 19:31.220
so we ended up sleeping on the street.

19:31.250 --> 19:34.350
Please forgive us for making a fool
of ourselves in front of you, Miss.

19:34.350 --> 19:36.150
Have you been like this every day

19:36.220 --> 19:37.420
for the past few days?

19:38.030 --> 19:38.880
Yes.

19:39.350 --> 19:40.610
We have to hit the road,

19:40.880 --> 19:42.450
so we'll take our leave first.

19:42.450 --> 19:43.170
Let's go.

19:50.270 --> 19:51.420
Young Master Qiyan,

19:51.440 --> 19:53.770
is this how you merchants make your money?

19:54.350 --> 19:55.480
When demand exceeds supply,

19:55.480 --> 19:57.000
prices naturally rise.

19:57.030 --> 19:58.300
That's just how things work.

19:58.300 --> 20:00.900
I won't stand in others' way
of making a profit.

20:02.680 --> 20:04.530
I appreciate your kindness,

20:04.640 --> 20:05.690
but I, Fan Yun, am not capable enough

20:05.690 --> 20:07.020
to take on such an important role.

20:07.020 --> 20:08.820
You'd better find someone else.

20:09.090 --> 20:10.150
I'll take my leave.

20:11.570 --> 20:12.290
Fan Yun!

20:22.480 --> 20:23.350
Fan Yun!

20:23.350 --> 20:24.400
Governor.

20:24.400 --> 20:25.660
Why do you want to see me

20:25.700 --> 20:26.560
in such a hurry?

20:26.590 --> 20:27.290
Governor.

20:27.790 --> 20:30.390
I have something to report
to Your Excellency.

20:31.780 --> 20:33.180
Y... "Your Excellency"?

20:34.110 --> 20:35.460
I'm not used to you

20:35.590 --> 20:36.990
addressing me like that.

20:37.190 --> 20:38.820
It's been so long
since I left the Qi Residence.

20:38.820 --> 20:41.240
I should at least have some
proper etiquette, right?

20:41.240 --> 20:42.520
That's not important.

20:42.680 --> 20:43.310
I really have something

20:43.310 --> 20:44.830
important to tell you.

20:45.460 --> 20:47.010
The inns are exploiting the situation
by raising prices arbitrarily.

20:47.010 --> 20:48.830
Many students from humble backgrounds
who came for the exam

20:48.830 --> 20:50.110
can't afford to stay in the inns,

20:50.110 --> 20:52.450
so they have no choice but
to sleep on the streets.

20:52.450 --> 20:53.890
If that's true,

20:54.440 --> 20:55.680
it must be thoroughly investigated.

20:55.680 --> 20:56.350
Governor.

20:56.570 --> 20:57.480
I think

20:57.510 --> 20:58.770
it's not just the inns.

20:59.070 --> 21:01.750
Candidates are affected in terms of food,
clothing, shelter, and transportation.

21:01.750 --> 21:05.210
All these other areas
should also be carefully investigated.

21:05.300 --> 21:06.560
You're right, Fan Yun.

21:07.220 --> 21:08.430
If that's the case,

21:08.760 --> 21:11.090
please handle it all together, Governor.

21:15.480 --> 21:16.050
Then,

21:16.830 --> 21:18.890
do you have anything else to say to me?

21:19.720 --> 21:20.400
Yes.

21:21.830 --> 21:22.830
I can't handle

21:22.830 --> 21:24.560
all these things by myself,

21:24.710 --> 21:26.900
so I asked Gao Ran and the others to help.

21:26.900 --> 21:28.100
They should be here

21:28.480 --> 21:29.530
by now.

21:32.430 --> 21:33.440
Nothing else?

21:36.960 --> 21:38.510
Well...

21:39.690 --> 21:40.770
Nothing else.

21:44.880 --> 21:45.880
Your Excellency.

21:50.090 --> 21:51.680
We're back from the investigation.

21:51.680 --> 21:53.930
All restaurants are only offering
"designated set meals,"

21:53.930 --> 21:55.510
claiming it saves time and effort,

21:55.510 --> 21:56.860
but in fact the quality of dishes
has been reduced

21:56.860 --> 21:57.920
while prices are effectively increased.

21:57.920 --> 21:59.780
Those peddlers selling fake exam questions

21:59.780 --> 22:01.130
are posing as private school teachers,

22:01.130 --> 22:02.550
scamming as many as they can.

22:02.550 --> 22:04.030
And the stationery shops selling
brushes, ink, paper, inkstones,

22:04.030 --> 22:05.030
and even books,

22:05.030 --> 22:06.400
have all raised their prices
by 7 or 8 times.

22:06.400 --> 22:07.550
Across the cities, both river
and land transport are overloaded.

22:07.550 --> 22:09.400
Ox carts, horse carriages—
all kinds of transport capacity is tight.

22:09.400 --> 22:11.310
In order to get to Ling'an
on time for the exam,

22:11.310 --> 22:12.920
the candidates have almost spent
all their travel expenses.

22:12.920 --> 22:13.340
That's right.

22:13.340 --> 22:14.640
Ox carts, horse carriages,
and donkey carts

22:14.640 --> 22:15.510
are all crammed together—
utter chaos.

22:15.510 --> 22:17.440
The scholars are being badly crushed
in the overcrowded conditions.

22:17.440 --> 22:18.770
It was truly miserable.

22:19.590 --> 22:20.720
This is outrageous.

22:21.790 --> 22:22.920
I never thought the selection exam
would become

22:22.920 --> 22:24.950
a means to oppress the common people.

22:24.950 --> 22:26.210
Governor, your original intention

22:26.210 --> 22:27.540
was not like this at all.

22:29.120 --> 22:30.080
If this goes on,

22:30.590 --> 22:32.790
you'll only lose the people's support.

22:37.640 --> 22:38.400
Governor.

22:39.200 --> 22:40.730
I actually have a solution.

22:43.030 --> 22:45.960
Lord Jiang Shu of the Commerce Bureau,
hear my order.

22:48.550 --> 22:49.940
Yes, Your Excellency.

22:50.480 --> 22:52.310
The selection exam is approaching.

22:52.310 --> 22:53.240
This initiative

22:53.480 --> 22:56.200
is to recruit talents
from across the Nine Cities

22:56.200 --> 22:57.800
and is of utmost importance.

22:57.850 --> 22:59.220
On top of that, this year's selection exam

22:59.220 --> 23:01.270
is very different from those of the past.

23:01.270 --> 23:03.270
The number of participants, scale,

23:03.920 --> 23:05.450
and the geographical scope

23:05.640 --> 23:07.200
are all unprecedented.

23:07.720 --> 23:10.650
To ensure the smooth conduct
of this selection exam,

23:11.110 --> 23:11.860
I hereby

23:12.110 --> 23:13.770
issue the following decrees.

23:14.270 --> 23:14.940
First,

23:15.200 --> 23:17.830
items related to the selection exam,
such as books, brushes,

23:17.830 --> 23:19.350
ink, paper, and inkstones

23:19.640 --> 23:21.640
must be strictly prohibited from
price gouging.

23:21.640 --> 23:23.330
[Zhonghe Restaurant]

23:22.160 --> 23:23.660
Furthermore, there must be tight regulation
of so-called "pre-exam guidance"

23:23.660 --> 23:26.620
that actually amounts to
selling leaked exam papers.

23:26.620 --> 23:27.540
[Qingchengzhai Stationery Shop]

23:26.830 --> 23:29.350
If any form of exorbitant pricing
is discovered,

23:29.350 --> 23:31.080
it should be severly punished.

23:31.680 --> 23:32.510
Second,

23:33.020 --> 23:35.450
to facilitate candidates traveling from
various regions to take the exam,

23:35.450 --> 23:37.920
special selection exam transport services
will be established.

23:37.920 --> 23:40.330
All candidates, upon presenting
their selection Exam Tokens,

23:40.330 --> 23:42.090
may ride for free and proceed directly

23:42.090 --> 23:44.350
to the examination academy for the exam.

23:44.400 --> 23:45.440
Third,

23:46.180 --> 23:47.830
this time, Huan'e House

23:47.920 --> 23:51.640
voluntarily opens its accommodations
free of charge to candidates.

23:51.640 --> 23:53.670
Candidates only need to present
their Exam Tokens, and may bring

23:53.670 --> 23:56.470
at most one accompanying person
to stay with them.

23:57.310 --> 23:58.590
If conditions permit,

23:58.850 --> 24:01.650
candidates may also bring
their own ingredients.

24:01.780 --> 24:03.170
Restaurants and inns

24:03.200 --> 24:05.460
should all open their kitchens for free,

24:05.560 --> 24:08.110
ensuring proper living conditions
for candidates,

24:08.110 --> 24:09.510
so they can perform

24:09.540 --> 24:11.210
at their best in the exam.

24:14.590 --> 24:16.030
I accept the order.

24:17.770 --> 24:18.680
Are you

24:18.700 --> 24:19.900
still upset?

24:22.410 --> 24:23.370
I'm not.

24:24.690 --> 24:26.050
Still refusing to tell me the truth.

24:26.050 --> 24:27.160
You know,

24:27.180 --> 24:29.250
if there's anything making you feel upset,

24:29.250 --> 24:30.710
or anything you want to let out—

24:30.710 --> 24:31.900
if you want to curse the Governor

24:31.900 --> 24:32.910
or just have a good cry—

24:32.910 --> 24:34.110
I'll be here with you.

24:37.640 --> 24:39.840
What does that mean, shaking your head?

24:39.910 --> 24:41.670
Actually, I just feel like

24:42.110 --> 24:42.940
I've been

24:43.510 --> 24:45.400
running toward a mountain peak
all this time,

24:45.400 --> 24:47.330
sprinting forward without stopping.

24:47.330 --> 24:48.960
But as I kept running,

24:48.990 --> 24:50.390
someone suddenly told me

24:50.610 --> 24:52.020
that the peak was gone.

24:53.550 --> 24:54.960
So I just

24:54.960 --> 24:56.510
lost my goal all of a sudden,

24:57.000 --> 24:58.170
and I just feel a bit

24:58.560 --> 25:00.650
empty inside, that's all.

25:01.440 --> 25:02.850
And I also believe

25:03.150 --> 25:04.600
that the Governor

25:04.890 --> 25:06.690
must have already done his best.

25:06.900 --> 25:08.610
So why should I blame him?

25:09.330 --> 25:10.360
Wait.

25:10.750 --> 25:12.030
I think

25:12.050 --> 25:14.600
I've just thought of something incredible.

25:15.240 --> 25:16.110
What is it?

25:18.510 --> 25:20.480
I know how to cheer you up.

25:23.000 --> 25:25.660
You should go back to
being the Governor's wife.

25:26.680 --> 25:27.810
-Right.
-Wait...

25:27.840 --> 25:28.960
What are you even talking about?

25:28.960 --> 25:31.070
You used to smile a lot
back at the Qi Residence.

25:31.070 --> 25:31.920
But now that

25:31.920 --> 25:32.960
you can't take the selection exam,

25:32.960 --> 25:34.290
this is the only way out.

25:34.790 --> 25:36.000
It's easy to go from rags to riches,

25:36.000 --> 25:37.720
but hard to go from riches to rags.

25:37.720 --> 25:39.030
Your house is too shabby,

25:39.030 --> 25:40.160
especially that table.

25:40.160 --> 25:40.960
If I were you,

25:40.960 --> 25:42.350
I wouldn't want to stay here either.

25:42.350 --> 25:43.170
What do you think?

25:43.170 --> 25:44.750
My proposal is not bad, right?

25:44.750 --> 25:46.350
Come and take a look.

25:46.350 --> 25:48.380
Why are there so many people
gathered over there?

25:48.380 --> 25:49.780
Let's go check it out.

25:50.360 --> 25:53.140
The stories of the Nine Noble Families
are known to all.

25:53.140 --> 25:55.900
You must be tired of hearing about them.

25:56.030 --> 25:58.310
Today, I will tell you something new.

26:00.510 --> 26:02.060
This story

26:02.110 --> 26:05.520
begins 13 years ago, when the princes
fought for the throne.

26:06.260 --> 26:09.370
-Great!
-Great!

26:18.560 --> 26:19.720
Thirteen years ago,

26:19.930 --> 26:21.160
after the late Governor passed away,

26:21.160 --> 26:22.820
his sons vied for succession.

26:22.830 --> 26:24.640
The Nine Cities, which had finally
enjoyed a few years of peace,

26:24.640 --> 26:25.920
were once again plunged into

26:25.920 --> 26:28.310
-It's the Governor.
-the chaos of war.

26:28.750 --> 26:31.920
Bravo! Bravo!

26:34.060 --> 26:36.060
The late governor's most favored

26:36.090 --> 26:38.010
and most outstanding
Second Young Master Qi,

26:38.010 --> 26:39.290
was framed

26:40.300 --> 26:42.500
and assassinated on the way into exile.

26:42.770 --> 26:44.090
His fate was unknown,

26:44.120 --> 26:45.780
and the odds were against him.

26:46.550 --> 26:48.810
Meanwhile, those elder brothers
who coveted the throne

26:48.810 --> 26:49.930
fought each other fiercely,

26:49.930 --> 26:51.530
all suffering heavy losses.

26:51.610 --> 26:54.000
In the end, it was the weakest

26:54.020 --> 26:55.210
and most incompetent youngest son,

26:55.210 --> 26:56.880
Qi Zheng—whom no one
had ever thought much of—

26:56.880 --> 26:59.330
who ended up benefiting from the chaos

27:00.110 --> 27:02.790
and became the new ruler
of the Nine Cities.

27:04.160 --> 27:05.680
But Qi Zheng

27:05.700 --> 27:07.510
wasn't necessarily that majestic.

27:07.510 --> 27:10.120
Even the secret guard unit personally
established by the late governor

27:10.120 --> 27:11.920
didn't swear allegiance to him.

27:11.990 --> 27:13.120
He was truly

27:13.140 --> 27:14.570
isolated and helpless,

27:14.640 --> 27:16.040
trudging forward alone.

27:18.400 --> 27:19.640
Although

27:20.350 --> 27:22.010
Qi Zheng was fortunate enough

27:22.510 --> 27:24.040
to become the new governor,

27:24.580 --> 27:26.410
a fool dressed in splendid robes

27:26.440 --> 27:29.170
can never truly become
gold or silver at his core.

27:29.590 --> 27:30.990
Moreover, he

27:31.240 --> 27:33.770
was arrogant and self-important,

27:34.350 --> 27:35.480
so it was inevitable

27:35.480 --> 27:38.440
that he would be jointly suppressed
by Lord Lyu and Lord Zheng.

27:38.440 --> 27:40.310
The "beatings" were like stir-frying
bamboo shoot with pork—

27:40.310 --> 27:41.910
refreshing and satisfying.

27:43.110 --> 27:44.220
Right at this time,

27:45.070 --> 27:46.510
the appearance of a woman

27:47.400 --> 27:48.880
changed everything.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.820
She and the Governor

27:52.850 --> 27:55.260
met under a phoenix tree.

27:55.280 --> 27:57.610
She took the Governor on incognito visits

27:57.790 --> 28:00.320
to empathize with the suffering
of the common people,

28:00.320 --> 28:01.680
and she encouraged him

28:02.000 --> 28:03.740
to fulfill the duties of his position

28:03.740 --> 28:05.140
and govern accordingly,

28:05.400 --> 28:07.860
and even in the face of
countless hardships,

28:07.960 --> 28:10.490
to keep his head held high
and strive forward.

28:10.550 --> 28:12.480
It was precisely because of
this woman's encouragement

28:12.480 --> 28:13.340
that Qi Zheng

28:13.960 --> 28:17.220
truly gained confidence and took up
the responsibilities of the governor,

28:17.220 --> 28:19.680
striving to become
a ruler of the Nine Cities

28:19.840 --> 28:20.860
who governed with the people's welfare
at heart—

28:20.860 --> 28:23.060
a wise and benevolent sovereign.

28:24.430 --> 28:25.630
As for this woman—

28:26.440 --> 28:28.040
she was the governor's wife,

28:28.140 --> 28:29.510
his trusted confidant,

28:29.540 --> 28:30.870
his sword and shield,

28:32.190 --> 28:33.970
always by his side in support.

28:35.060 --> 28:36.030
Yet she herself

28:36.640 --> 28:37.510
was never able

28:37.510 --> 28:39.510
to realize her own dream.

28:40.680 --> 28:42.460
This is where today's story ends.

28:42.460 --> 28:44.220
To be continued.

28:45.270 --> 28:49.340
Bravo! Bravo!

28:49.360 --> 28:53.070
Well performed! Bravo!

29:03.360 --> 29:04.850
♪ If women are akin to blossoms ♪

29:04.890 --> 29:07.230
♪ Can they be cherished tenderly? ♪

29:07.390 --> 29:10.560
♪ For whom do they hide tears silently? ♪

29:10.840 --> 29:13.060
♪ How could one bear to lay blame? ♪

29:13.080 --> 29:15.450
♪ Time runs wild with reckless haste ♪

29:15.480 --> 29:19.180
♪ Never mind that
fate dyes pureness crimson red ♪

29:19.490 --> 29:20.830
♪ For whom does ♪

29:19.640 --> 29:21.600
Alright, you've finished
listening to the story, right?

29:20.850 --> 29:23.020
♪ This phoenix flower bloom? ♪

29:21.630 --> 29:23.300
You can all disperse now.

29:23.050 --> 29:27.020
♪ Love fills my years,
and my heart remains true ♪

29:27.250 --> 29:29.300
♪ Let all worldly longing fade away ♪

29:29.330 --> 29:31.720
♪ Fall deep within a single dream ♪

29:31.970 --> 29:42.790
♪ Wait till a breath of wind arrives ♪

29:40.960 --> 29:43.240
She may never know

29:43.850 --> 29:45.180
how deeply the governor

29:45.540 --> 29:47.870
wished to help her realize her ambitions.

29:52.230 --> 29:54.960
But the road ahead was
long and full of obstacles,

29:55.400 --> 29:58.200
and the governor may have ultimately
let her down.

30:00.050 --> 30:00.960
Qi Zheng.

30:04.480 --> 30:06.050
You didn't let me down.

30:19.520 --> 30:20.650
Then do you blame me?

30:22.720 --> 30:23.550
Of course not.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.440
How could reform

30:28.660 --> 30:30.350
ever be achieved overnight?

30:33.160 --> 30:35.420
It definitely has to be done step by step.

30:36.480 --> 30:37.550
Besides,

30:38.200 --> 30:40.590
Governor, you've done a great job already.

30:40.590 --> 30:41.720
At least now,

30:41.720 --> 30:43.120
those commoner students

30:43.270 --> 30:45.030
finally have a path to
rise through the ranks.

30:45.030 --> 30:45.980
That proves

30:46.310 --> 30:48.030
all your efforts up to this point

30:48.030 --> 30:49.230
haven't been in vain.

30:50.290 --> 30:51.690
As for me,

30:52.640 --> 30:53.680
I...

30:55.010 --> 30:56.600
do feel a bit upset.

30:58.720 --> 31:00.030
But

31:00.680 --> 31:01.920
I still have you

31:02.640 --> 31:03.920
by my side, don't I?

31:08.680 --> 31:11.410
That's even more reason
why we shouldn't give up.

31:11.750 --> 31:12.780
I can't give up—

31:13.550 --> 31:15.350
and you certainly can't either.

31:15.920 --> 31:17.050
If even we ourselves

31:17.550 --> 31:19.170
believe that women
cannot serve as officials,

31:19.170 --> 31:21.370
then who else would believe otherwise?

31:21.960 --> 31:22.870
So, Fan Yun,

31:24.040 --> 31:24.890
I hope

31:25.600 --> 31:27.120
you can give me some time

31:28.120 --> 31:29.390
and let me try again,

31:29.450 --> 31:30.120
okay?

31:33.980 --> 31:34.640
Okay.

31:35.730 --> 31:36.440
This is bad!

31:37.040 --> 31:38.700
Something happened outside!

31:39.880 --> 31:41.390
What exactly is going on?

31:42.750 --> 31:45.240
I was walking when I suddenly
got knocked down,

31:45.240 --> 31:46.970
and my Exam Token disappeared.

31:47.070 --> 31:48.350
He was even more unfortunate.

31:48.350 --> 31:49.720
His Exam Token got snatched,

31:49.720 --> 31:51.380
and he was beaten up like this.

31:53.730 --> 31:55.020
Who is so brazen

31:55.590 --> 31:57.070
as to openly snatch Exam Tokens

31:57.070 --> 31:58.870
and disrupt the selection exam?

32:04.580 --> 32:05.130
Here.

32:09.760 --> 32:10.890
Wait for me a moment.

32:11.170 --> 32:12.570
I'll go get another medicine for you.

32:12.570 --> 32:13.340
Use this.

32:16.590 --> 32:18.480
This is a secret ointment
from my hometown.

32:18.480 --> 32:19.350
You can try it.

32:19.350 --> 32:20.060
Really?

32:20.350 --> 32:21.310
Thank you.

32:22.160 --> 32:22.770
Here.

32:34.890 --> 32:36.290
Bear with it for a moment.

32:36.880 --> 32:37.640
Done.

32:44.240 --> 32:45.440
After you go back,

32:45.550 --> 32:47.280
make sure to get some good rest.

32:47.330 --> 32:47.950
Okay.

32:48.940 --> 32:50.070
Thank you, Miss.

32:50.150 --> 32:51.050
Thank you, Sir.

32:52.090 --> 32:52.680
Let's go.

32:59.610 --> 33:00.570
Young Healer,

33:00.600 --> 33:01.640
are you

33:01.660 --> 33:03.050
hurt anywhere?

33:03.970 --> 33:04.770
I'm okay.

33:05.640 --> 33:06.750
I've long admired you, Teacher.

33:06.750 --> 33:08.410
I, Tian Xing, pay my respects.

33:09.850 --> 33:10.850
Young Healer,

33:10.870 --> 33:12.150
do you always talk

33:12.200 --> 33:13.510
in such a bookish way?

33:14.590 --> 33:15.350
And,

33:15.640 --> 33:17.370
how did you know that I was...

33:17.390 --> 33:18.390
My companion said

33:18.420 --> 33:19.640
you are a female teacher.

33:19.640 --> 33:21.090
You're no less capable than any man.

33:21.090 --> 33:23.750
Not only did you set up a private school
for commoner students,

33:23.750 --> 33:24.820
but you also teach them
literature and propriety

33:24.820 --> 33:26.270
with remarkable literary talent.

33:26.270 --> 33:27.240
I've heard

33:27.570 --> 33:29.190
you also once taught the governor.

33:29.190 --> 33:32.520
You are said to be the best teacher
in the entire Nine Cities.

33:33.370 --> 33:35.230
I'm flattered. Truly flattered.

33:36.300 --> 33:36.900
By the way,

33:37.200 --> 33:38.570
I haven't asked you

33:38.720 --> 33:39.720
what your name is.

33:41.110 --> 33:42.030
I am Tian Xing,

33:42.480 --> 33:44.400
and I also want to take you as my teacher.

33:44.400 --> 33:45.810
Tian Xing...

33:48.030 --> 33:48.940
Please

33:49.240 --> 33:51.240
just keep calling me Young Healer.

33:52.130 --> 33:52.920
Alright,

33:52.940 --> 33:53.740
Young Healer.

33:55.110 --> 33:57.640
Then let me officially
introduce myself too.

33:57.690 --> 33:58.820
My name is Fan Yun.

33:58.850 --> 34:00.000
If there's a chance,

34:00.070 --> 34:03.000
we can exchange knowledge
and learn from each other.

34:04.180 --> 34:05.180
Young Healer.

34:05.210 --> 34:07.270
I still have some things to attend to.

34:07.310 --> 34:09.170
Let's have tea and talk next time.

34:12.530 --> 34:13.699
Take care, Teacher.

34:19.630 --> 34:20.510
You mean

34:20.960 --> 34:22.670
the ones who stole the Exam Tokens

34:22.670 --> 34:24.690
are an organization
called the Shadow Slay League?

34:24.690 --> 34:25.290
Yes.

34:25.780 --> 34:28.600
The Shadow Slay League used to be
a band of bandits roaming the mountains.

34:28.600 --> 34:29.929
They specialize in robbing

34:29.929 --> 34:32.500
merchant caravans
transporting goods across cities,

34:32.500 --> 34:35.100
and they all have high bounties
on their heads.

34:35.710 --> 34:38.320
So it seems someone is trying to hire
the Shadow Slay League

34:38.320 --> 34:40.120
to sabotage the selection exam.

34:40.630 --> 34:42.330
That's also what I guessed.

34:43.550 --> 34:44.510
I see.

34:45.400 --> 34:45.830
Hu Die,

34:46.570 --> 34:47.810
now all the candidates

34:47.810 --> 34:49.260
are temporarily staying at Huan'e House.

34:49.260 --> 34:50.449
Since something like this happened,

34:50.449 --> 34:52.310
we must strengthen precautions.

35:15.740 --> 35:17.490
You are so strong!

35:25.700 --> 35:26.930
This is weird.

35:27.800 --> 35:30.110
You were alone in this room,

35:30.860 --> 35:32.390
so why did you lock the door?

35:35.720 --> 35:36.600
Look,

35:37.070 --> 35:38.550
is it red from the bump?

35:38.670 --> 35:39.670
Blow on it for me.

35:46.130 --> 35:47.100
Why is there

35:47.870 --> 35:50.100
a scent of face powder in this room?

35:50.450 --> 35:51.200
Face powder?

35:52.380 --> 35:53.310
I don't smell it.

35:53.670 --> 35:54.490
Maybe it's yours.

35:54.490 --> 35:55.360
Nonsense.

35:55.670 --> 35:57.730
I didn't put on any face powder today.

36:05.230 --> 36:06.060
I know!

36:06.150 --> 36:07.870
It's Hu Die's scent.

36:13.410 --> 36:14.770
Could it be

36:14.800 --> 36:15.990
that

36:17.720 --> 36:18.800
you two...

36:18.820 --> 36:20.380
You two are...

36:22.230 --> 36:23.630
Absolutely impossible.

36:23.630 --> 36:25.030
Absolutely impossible!

36:25.880 --> 36:27.240
Why so nervous?

36:37.100 --> 36:38.170
Still denying it?

36:38.200 --> 36:39.200
Then what's this?

36:47.360 --> 36:48.290
Are you jealous?

36:52.520 --> 36:53.210
I...

36:54.730 --> 36:56.790
What nonsense are you talking about?

36:57.080 --> 37:00.130
I think you must have
knocked yourself stupid

37:00.160 --> 37:01.590
from that bump just now.

37:03.530 --> 37:04.890
I won't tease you anymore.

37:04.890 --> 37:05.950
This handkerchief

37:06.110 --> 37:07.510
indeed belongs to Hu Die.

37:07.880 --> 37:08.900
But don't you want to know

37:08.900 --> 37:10.360
what she came to see me for?

37:12.570 --> 37:13.380
I don't.

37:13.410 --> 37:14.330
That won't do.

37:15.280 --> 37:16.510
You must know.

37:17.140 --> 37:17.880
Come out.

37:20.070 --> 37:21.110
What?

37:21.920 --> 37:24.650
You're saying the real owner
behind Huan'e House

37:24.670 --> 37:26.210
is actually the Governor?

37:26.520 --> 37:27.650
-Yes.
-Hu Die.

37:29.250 --> 37:31.480
Have the accounting office calculate
how much commission she earned

37:31.480 --> 37:33.230
from bringing gullible customers

37:33.230 --> 37:34.630
to spend at Huan'e House,

37:34.670 --> 37:35.610
and have her return it immediately.

37:35.610 --> 37:36.340
Then...

37:37.400 --> 37:39.080
What's wrong with you?

37:39.100 --> 37:41.100
Why are you digging up old debts now?

37:41.730 --> 37:43.480
Our top priority right now

37:43.500 --> 37:45.700
should be standing united
against outsiders, shouldn't it?

37:45.700 --> 37:47.440
Why should I stand united with you?

37:47.440 --> 37:49.150
It's not like you're my wife or something.

37:49.150 --> 37:49.700
I...

37:50.490 --> 37:52.380
Hu Die just said

37:52.410 --> 37:54.270
that it was an organization
called the Shadow Slay League

37:54.270 --> 37:55.570
who stole the Exam Tokens.

37:55.570 --> 37:57.900
We should work together to deal with them.

37:59.110 --> 38:00.840
Don't you agree, Hu Die?

38:03.440 --> 38:05.210
When did Hu Die leave?

38:09.710 --> 38:10.730
How about this?

38:11.210 --> 38:12.000
I'll

38:12.030 --> 38:13.240
come up with a plan

38:13.260 --> 38:14.920
to help you catch the thieves,

38:14.920 --> 38:15.920
and we'll use that

38:16.230 --> 38:17.550
to offset the commission.

38:17.550 --> 38:18.680
How does that sound?

38:19.960 --> 38:21.920
You already had this planned out,
didn't you?

38:21.920 --> 38:24.650
This is exactly
what you came to Huan'e House for.

38:28.840 --> 38:29.640
Go ahead then.

38:30.120 --> 38:31.350
Let's see if your plan

38:31.550 --> 38:32.610
is worth the money.

38:33.800 --> 38:35.000
Don't worry about it.

38:35.280 --> 38:36.010
Just leave it to me.
